List of things I'm planning to do.

  * - soon
  o - later


Runtime library
---------------

* comparison interface; give compare virtual method an extra parameter
  to tell if it is called for comparison or just for equivalence checking.

* class copy protocol

* general hash table interface

o serial.c: realize native serializer.

Compiler and VM
---------------

* Allow to define inlinable procedure (maybe in conjunction with case-lambda)

* better inliner definition for genstub

o Method cache.  Each VM to have a table that maps (gf, targs ...) => sorted
  method list.  Invalidated if any of method of gf is redefined.
  Keep it in VM rather than gf makes MT easier.

o Stack garbage collection.
  

Modules
-------

* extension dbm : dbm interface

* module dbi/* : unified DB interface

* module gauche.lock :general file locking

* module file.utils : common file utils

* module file.find 

* module file.du

* module math/mt-random : Mersenne Twister random number generator

* module math/perlin-noise : Ken Perlin's noise function

* module math/quat : Quaternions

* module math/matrix : Matrices

* module rfc/http : http parsing

* module rfc/smtp : smtp interface

* module rfc/ftp : ftp interface

o module w3c/xml : xml parsing

